@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v0 + (wp.sin(v0 + 0.12) * tmp))
    v1 = (v0 + wp.exp((tmp + 0.53 - v2 + 0.91)))
    v2 = (0.86 / v0)
    v2 = ((v1 + tmp) * (v0 / 0.23))
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.cos(v0 + 0.25) - (v2 + 0.19 + v2 + 0.36)))
    data[tid] = v0
